Download from http://www.mongodb.org/downloads
Install .msi file in folder C:\mongo-data
Create data, data\db, log directories and mongo.config file under C:\mongodb.
Add the following lines in "mongo.config" file
dbpath=C:\mongo-data\data\db\
logpath=C:\mongo-data\log\mongo.log
Start server :
mongod.exe --config="C:\mongo-data\mongo.config"


1)
cd C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.4\bin

2)
mongo.exe
or
mongod.exe --dbpath/~/mongo-data/data/db

